[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":223},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F":200,"related:\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F":209},"\u002Fen\u002Fhexo\u002F2020\u002F10\u002F31\u002Flearn-hexo-32-updating-hexo\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":183,"date":184,"description":18,"extension":185,"lang":186,"meta":187,"navigation":188,"path":189,"readingMinutes":190,"seo":191,"standalone":192,"stem":193,"tags":194,"tldr":197,"updated":197,"url":198,"__hash__":199},"content\u002F試著學 Hexo\u002F32-試著學-Hexo-番外篇之更新-Hexo.md","(32)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 Hexo","2194088152",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":175},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,36,39,42,51,68,83,87,90,109,112,117,120,124,127,145,148,155,158,161,164,171],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"更新這件事情其實非常的重要，但 Hexo 在更新上是真的非常麻煩，所以額外撰寫了番外篇來介紹如何更新 Hexo。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"更新-hexo","更新 Hexo",[16,24,25],{},"在我撰寫「試著學 Hexo」系列的時候，其實 Hexo 已經默默從 Hexo4 更新到 Hexo5，因此本篇我就會直接從 Hexo 3.9.0 跳到 Hexo 5.2.0。",[16,27,28],{},"在前面其實有說過 Hexo 在更新上非常的麻煩，那麻煩程度是什麼呢？其實就是直接重新建立一個 Hexo 啦",[16,30,31],{},[32,33],"img",{"alt":34,"src":35},"WT...","https:\u002F\u002Fi.imgur.com\u002Fzwbkhhv.png",[16,37,38],{},"在此我會建議先更新自己本身電腦的 Hexo CLI 才可以唷(目前版本是 4.2.0)",[16,40,41],{},"(這邊要注意 Hexo5 必須要 Node.js 10 以上才能運作唷。)",[16,43,44,45,50],{},"安裝完畢之後基本上流程與「",[46,47,49],"a",{"href":48},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20200917\u002F636983586\u002F","試著學 Hexo - 認識 Hexo 目錄結構","」差不多，所以以下就快速貼上指令帶過",[52,53,58],"pre",{"className":54,"code":55,"language":56,"meta":57,"style":57},"language-cmd shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","hexo init blog # 部落格名稱自訂\n","cmd","",[59,60,61],"code",{"__ignoreMap":57},[62,63,66],"span",{"class":64,"line":65},"line",1,[62,67,55],{},[16,69,70,71,74,75,78,79,82],{},"建立完畢後打開 package.json 就可以看到 ",[59,72,73],{},"dependencies"," 中的 ",[59,76,77],{},"\"hexo\""," 是顯示 ",[59,80,81],{},"5.0.0","。",[12,84,86],{"id":85},"調整-_configyml","調整 _config.yml",[16,88,89],{},"更新這一段 _config.yml 是非常麻煩的，而且又不能直接複製貼上，因此新版 Hexo 調整了非常多地方，建議使用一些比對工具來重新回填",[91,92,93,102],"ul",{},[94,95,96],"li",{},[46,97,101],{"href":98,"rel":99},"https:\u002F\u002Fdiffnow.com\u002Fcompare-clips",[100],"nofollow","diffnow",[94,103,104],{},[46,105,108],{"href":106,"rel":107},"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.diffchecker.com\u002Fdiff",[100],"diffchecker",[16,110,111],{},"其實網路上比對工具滿多的，所以挑選自己習慣的就好了",[16,113,114],{},[32,115],{"alt":108,"src":116},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002FHexo\u002F%E8%A9%A6%E8%91%97%E5%AD%B8%20Hexo%20%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202020-10-31%2014.28.47.png",[16,118,119],{},"(這一段相對麻煩很多，但如果你想體驗到 Hexo 最新的話，那就只能認命。)",[12,121,123],{"id":122},"hexo-5-與-hexo-4-差異","Hexo 5 與 Hexo 4 差異",[16,125,126],{},"在最新版來講，編譯速度是不用多說，就是有提升，如果你跟我一樣是使用舊版 3.9.0 的人，在更新到 Hexo 5 或 4 之後會有很大的感受（尤其是文章有破百篇的狀況下）",[16,128,129,130,133,134,137,138,141,142,144],{},"但是在這邊我自己覺得 Hexo 5 之後最大特色大概就是主題終於使用 ",[59,131,132],{},"npm"," 來安裝而不是使用 ",[59,135,136],{},"git clone","，當然 Hexo 5 還是有保留原有的 ",[59,139,140],{},"theme\u002F[主題名稱]"," 建立方式，但有好 ",[59,143,132],{}," 你能不用嗎？",[16,146,147],{},"除此之外這次高亮不再只有 highlight.js 也加入了 Prism.js 所以整個功能上也大大的提升，其他的部分你可以去看官網解釋比較快",[16,149,150],{},[46,151,154],{"href":152,"rel":153},"https:\u002F\u002Fhexo.io\u002Fnews\u002F2020\u002F07\u002F29\u002Fhexo-5-released\u002F",[100],"Hexo 5.0.0 Released",[16,156,157],{},"基本上在設置上是沒有太大差異，所以這邊就不花太多時間介紹 _config.yml",[16,159,160],{},"我必須說更新這條路真的是坑，尤其是主題這部分，但這次的 Hexo 5 更新，其實對於主題的更新上就方便許多，所以下一篇就會來針對 NexT 的更新來介紹，那如果你是 Hexo 3.9.0，我是真心建議你可以更新到至少 Hexo 4，整體編譯速度上真的快超多。",[12,162,163],{"id":163},"參考文獻",[91,165,166],{},[94,167,168],{},[46,169,154],{"href":152,"rel":170},[100],[172,173,174],"style",{},"html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}",{"title":57,"searchDepth":176,"depth":176,"links":177},2,[178,179,180,181,182],{"id":14,"depth":176,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":176,"text":22},{"id":85,"depth":176,"text":86},{"id":122,"depth":176,"text":123},{"id":163,"depth":176,"text":163},"Hexo","2020-10-31 14:01:51","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fhexo\u002F32-hexo-hexo","2",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"試著學 Hexo\u002F32-試著學-Hexo-番外篇之更新-Hexo",[183,195,196],"試著學 Hexo","第 12 屆 iT邦幫忙鐵人賽",null,"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201031\u002F2194088152\u002F","YKwpbma2sXeLXG4RBC3KGOp1Jb5LQZLpocBI4KSh4GM",{"newer":201,"older":205},{"url":202,"title":203,"date":204},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201031\u002F3727169327\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (38) - TexturePacker","2020-10-31 14:56:47",{"url":206,"title":207,"date":208},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20201021\u002F1504709600\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (37) - 加入 stats.js","2020-10-21 15:25:20",[210,214,219],{"url":211,"title":212,"date":213,"readingMinutes":190},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20221030\u002F561405053\u002F","解決 Hexo 更新系統或使用 CI 部署後文章出現更新日期的問題","2022-10-30 11:52:35",{"url":215,"title":216,"date":217,"readingMinutes":218},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201101\u002F60919\u002F","(33)試著學 Hexo-番外篇之更新 NexT 主題","2020-11-01 13:21:00","3",{"url":220,"title":221,"date":222,"readingMinutes":190},"\u002Fhexo\u002F20201014\u002F642399884\u002F","(31) 試著學 Hexo - 番外篇之常見問題","2020-10-14 00:00:01",1784020386152]